        "description": {
            "name": "description",
            "type": "java.lang.String",
            "value": "It would be nice to have the option to send json-comment-filtered (meaning between \/* and *\/) when using $this->_helper->autoCompleteDojo($data).   I had this message from Dojo: \"please consider using a mimetype of text\/json-comment-filtered to avoid potential security issues with JSON endpoints (use djConfig.usePlainJson=true to turn off this message)\" as described here: \nhttp:\/\/dojotoolkit.org\/forum\/dijit-dijit-0-9\/dijit-support\/text-json-comment-filtered#comment-5853."
